    "text": "Justice Reinvestment Initiative Act of 2019\n\nThis bill provides statutory authority for the Justice Reinvestment Initiative grant program within the Department of Justice. The program provides grants to states, local governments, Indian tribes, and entities and institutions of higher education with national law enforcement and corrections expertise to analyze criminal justice trends and increase public safety by allocating resources to efforts that reduce crime and recidivism."
